‘z f’ (‘magit-stash-format-patch’)
     Create a patch from STASH.

‘k’ (‘magit-stash-clear’)
     Remove all stashes saved in REF’s reflog by deleting REF.

‘z l’ (‘magit-stash-list’)
     List all stashes in a buffer.

